// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3106 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 3320a23b-e954-5f41-86c5-5261379556bc

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*")
